
    Ambani-Piramal wedding: Beyoncé sings at A-list Indian event

        

    
        
                
                Image copyright
                 Instagram/Beyonce
                
            
            
            Image caption
                
                    Beyoncé showed off her outfit on Instagram
                
            US singer Beyoncé has performed as part of the lavish festivities at the latest extravagant Indian celebrity wedding.Isha Ambani, the daughter of India's richest man, is tying the knot with Anand Piramal, son of another Indian billionaire, this week. Beyoncé was one of many celebrities flown in, along with Bollywood stars and figures like Hillary Clinton. It comes on the heels of several recent Indian weddings competing for glamour, excess and attention.The Ambanis themselves recently attended the wedding of Bollywood actors Deepika Padukone and Ranveer Singh. 
    
        
And last weekend, Isha Ambani was a bridesmaid at the wedding of actress Priyanka Chopra to US singer Nick Jonas.
    
        
