        The actual wedding of the daughter of business tycoon Mukesh Ambani is on Wednesday but the festivities leading up it kicked off over the weekend. Likely to be one of India's richest and most glamorous weddings, the many guests include former US First Lady and 2016 presidential candidate Hillary Clinton, media giant Arianna Huffington, cricketer Sachin Tendulkar and steel tycoon Lakshmi Mittal.India's richest family caps year of big fat weddings
